No. 1074,

Misc.

Mathis v. Wainwright, Corrections Director. Petitioner pro se. Earl Faircloth, Attorney General of Florida, and T. T. Turnbull, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted and the judgment reversed.
